---
// Hero component for overseas bank account closure service
---

<section class="p-6 sm:p-12" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Service">
  <div
    class="animate-reveal-from-left relative h-[calc(100vsh-3rem)] rounded-2xl bg-[url(../assets/images/hero_sm.jpg)] bg-cover bg-no-repeat sm:h-[calc(100vh-6rem)] sm:bg-[url(../assets/images/hero.jpg)]"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center p-6 sm:justify-start sm:pl-12"
    >
      <div>
        <h2
          class="animate-slide-in-left from-primary-500 to-primary-700 mb-2 bg-gradient-to-r bg-clip-text text-2xl font-bold text-transparent opacity-0 sm:mb-4 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
          itemprop="name"
        >
          海外口座、<br />放置していませんか？
        </h2>
        <h3
          class="animate-slide-in-left from-primary-600 to-primary-800 animate-delay-200 bg-gradient-to-r bg-clip-text text-sm font-semibold text-transparent opacity-0 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
        >
          <strong>
            現地渡航不要！英語力不要！<br
              class="block sm:hidden"
            />面倒な解約手続きをプロが完全サポート
          </strong>
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="animate-slide-in-up animate-delay-600 absolute right-0 bottom-0 rounded-tl-xl bg-white pt-4 pr-0 pb-0 pl-6 text-right opacity-0 sm:rounded-tl-2xl sm:pt-6 sm:pl-8"
    >
      <ul
        class="animate-fade-in-up from-primary-500 to-primary-700 animate-delay-1000 mb-2 bg-gradient-to-r bg-clip-text text-base font-bold text-transparent opacity-0 sm:mb-3 sm:text-xl"
      >
        <li>
          <strong>現地に行かずに、閉じられます！</strong>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>
            もちろん口座内の預金は
            <br class="block sm:hidden" />
            ご指定の銀行口座に送金可能
          </strong>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p
        class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-1400 text-xs opacity-0 sm:text-sm"
      >
        口座凍結・州政府移管・相続手続き…
        <br />
        複雑な海外口座の問題を、
        <br class="block sm:hidden" />
        実績多数の専門チームが解決します。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
